Team Lead Employee Services - Mobilink
Islamabad
Hold at least a Bachelor’s Degree or Master’s degree in Information Systems.
Have at least 3 years of relevant work experience
Supervise contractual employee services team.
Ensure provision of best employee services in line with policies and SOPs.
Ensure up-to-date employee records in systems and files.
Manage HRMS administration.
Monitor personnel hiring and termination timelines.
Manage employee group life insurance and associated claims.
Monitor monthly HR KPI achievement.
Settle final verification and coordination with project POCs & payroll team for smooth execution of payroll and final settlements.
Manage monthly inputs for payroll team.
Verify data periodically and conduct audit of HRMS.
Generate monthly reports for management.
Reconcile vendor’s statement of accounts for employee insurances.
Develop turnover report for medical and life insurance vendors for accurate invoicing.
Prepare miscellaneous analysis and reports as for management as per requirements.
Manage provision of other employee services and addressing employee queries.
Keep the audit area worthy at all times.
Identify and anticipate client needs and make recommendations for implementation
